short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Quickly find DevDocs without wasting a tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows you to quickly open a tab and get straight into DevDocs.io even without an internet connection. It removes the need for a pinned tab and allows easy access to a great developer resource.
